room_title: Escape room "Dr. Eugene's Diagnosis" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
room_description:
Dr. Eugene has been working for Doctors Without Borders in the Middle East. Dr. Eugene has been working on an antibiotic for an aggressive strain of plague but fell ill with the virus himself. You must complete his research and create the antibiotic to save the doctor.
If that wasn't enough, you've just received intel that one of the doctors in the local hospital has been working with a terrorist organization. Can you find a way to escape the hospital before the biological attack?
